    "We also examine the effects of additional investments in employerprovided chatbots and training.",
    "At the individual level, we also analyze heterogeneity by intensity of use and reported gains.",
    "A second key concern is that adopters may have fared differently in the labor market even without AI chatbots.",
    "We take two steps to address this issue.",
    "First, we control for workers' pre-determined characteristics-including gender, age, and labor market experience-to ensure these factors do not drive our estimates (e.g., adopters being younger and naturally on upward earnings trajectories)."
